e boss tries to oust the BOFH and the PFY again. Enter George, some lager, a shredder and several PFYs to-be... |last=Travaglia |first=Simon |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219055722/http://bofh.ntk.net/BOFH/1997/bastard97-30.php |archivedate=2014-12-19 }}</ref>
